title: Best scene from person of interest! Machine helps John escape
author: Keshav Kaanth
comment: This Show was ahead of it's time..

“Are you out of your mind?!?”
“Since when is that relevant.”

Oh root, how I love thee.
Honestly, detective fusco is actually iconic. They turned a throwaway side character into someone with genuine depth and someone we can root for. Honest to god this show ended too soon
